<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.rpgdot.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=5871">www.rpgdot.com/phpBB2/vie...php?t=5871</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Seems to argue you put your least used skills higher in the food chain because they get more bonuses to advance. Athletics should arguably be nothing but a misc skill regardless of build due to its heavy use and native propensity to advance. GAH! Another reroll.<br>
<br>
