<br>
Sneak is at 75+, Short Blade 80, Security 90, Destruction 80, Acrobat 85.<br>
<br>
With items Strength, Intelligence and Agility are all over 100.<br>
<br>
Beat the Archmage in a duel last night so the new one would be me. Man, he had nice stuff. Almost the Master Thief as well, maybe tonight...<br>
<br>
Got a whole set of glass armor courtesy of the 5 finger discount with duplicate pieces stashed away in case the theft ever catches up with me. Got an Ebony Short Sword that hits like a freight train. Make friends with the Khajit in Pelagiad. She knows some things that are very useful and will test your thieving abilities sorely. There are some Robin Hood-ish quests from the Master Thief in Vivec that are kind of fun.<br>
<br>
Picked up a matched set of plate gauntlets with a permanent effect of +20 STR on one and +20 Agil on the other. They nicely complement the Robe worth 40g (?!!?) I found. Fits over armor nicely and has a permanent effect of Regen Stamina and Regen Health +15 each. Can run full speed while jumping and it never hardly moves the bar.<br>
<br>
Stealth is awesome at higher levels. I was dispatching heavily armored opponents easily if I could get the drop on them. Most fights went something like this:<br>
<br>
(tiptoe sound)....SHANK...&quot;You should have picked an easier opponen.....cough...gak&quot; (fit of almost silent giggling and then more tiptoe sounds)<br>
<br>
